findings.fix_suggestion:
Convert all TTF files to WOFF2 using woff2_compress or an online converter. Update fonts.css:
@font-face {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display';
  src: url('/fonts/playfair-400.woff2') format('woff2'),
       url('/fonts/playfair-400.ttf') format('truetype');
}
WOFF2 has 97%+ browser support.

